na%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171231%2F57648122&h=06bb9bf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171231/57648122</a>"},{"pid":"b3d3461f5cf93c88db892be26ad4fa9143bffbea","tid":516224,"uid":99582,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T09:49:39.000Z","msg":"台日友好!?<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}